<% content_for(:title, "Privacy Policy - Crewbase") %>
<% meta_description "Crewbase privacy policy. How we collect, use, and protect your personal information." %>

<%# ===== HERO ===== %>
<section class="bg-[#0F224F] pt-10 pb-16">
  <div class="max-w-screen-xl mx-auto px-6">
    <p class="text-blue-200/60 text-sm font-medium mb-2">Legal</p>
    <h1 class="font-headline text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold text-white leading-[1.1] tracking-tight mb-4 max-w-2xl">
      Privacy Policy
    </h1>
    <p class="text-blue-200/80 text-base md:text-lg max-w-lg">
      Last updated: <%= Date.current.strftime("%d %B %Y") %>
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="bg-white py-16">
  <div class="max-w-screen-xl mx-auto px-6">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto prose-slate">

      <div class="space-y-10">
        <div>
          <h2 class="font-headline text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">1. Who we are</h2>
          <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            Crewbase is an accommodation marketplace connecting workers and contractors with hosts who have properties near job sites. When we say "we", "us", or "our", we mean Crewbase. When we say "you", we mean anyone who uses our website.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-headline text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">2. What information we collect</h2>
          <div class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed space-y-3">
            <p><strong class="text-slate-900">Account information:</strong> Your name, email address, and password when you sign up. If you're a host, we also collect your property details and payment information.</p>
            <p><strong class="text-slate-900">Booking information:</strong> Dates, guest counts, property selections, and payment details when you make a booking.</p>
            <p><strong class="text-slate-900">Messages:</strong> Any messages you send through our messaging system to hosts or guests.</p>
            <p><strong class="text-slate-900">Usage data:</strong> How you use our website — pages visited, search queries, and similar technical data.</p>
            <p><strong class="text-slate-900">Contact form submissions:</strong> Your name, email, and message when you use our contact form.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-headline text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">3. How we use your information</h2>
          <div class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed space-y-2">
            <p>We use your information to:</p>
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-2">
              <li>Create and manage your account</li>
              <li>Process bookings and payments</li>
              <li>Send booking confirmations and invoices</li>
              <li>Enable messaging between guests and hosts</li>
              <li>Respond to your enquiries and support requests</li>
              <li>Improve our website and services</li>
              <li>Prevent fraud and keep our site secure</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-headline text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">4. Who we share it with</h2>
          <div class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed space-y-3">
            <p><strong class="text-slate-900">Hosts and guests:</strong> When you make a booking, we share relevant details with the host (your name, booking dates, guest count). Hosts' property details and reviews are visible to guests.</p>
            <p><strong class="text-slate-900">Payment providers:</strong> We use secure payment processing to handle transactions. Your card details are handled by our payment provider — we don't store them ourselves.</p>
            <p><strong class="text-slate-900">Service providers:</strong> We may use third-party services to help run our website (hosting, email, analytics). They only access your data as needed to provide their services.</p>
            <p>We don't sell your personal information to anyone.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-headline text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">5. How we protect your data</h2>
          <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            We use industry-standard security measures to protect your information, including encryption for data in transit and secure storage for data at rest. Payments are processed through PCI-compliant payment providers.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-headline text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">6. Your rights</h2>
          <div class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed space-y-2">
            <p>You have the right to:</p>
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-2">
              <li>Access the personal data we hold about you</li>
              <li>Correct any inaccurate information</li>
              <li>Request deletion of your account and data</li>
              <li>Object to how we process your data</li>
              <li>Withdraw consent at any time</li>
            </ul>
            <p class="mt-3">To exercise any of these rights, <%= link_to "contact us", contact_path, class: "text-[#0F224F] font-medium underline hover:text-[#002d75]" %>.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-headline text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">7. Cookies</h2>
          <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            We use cookies to keep you logged in and to make the site work properly. For more details, see our <%= link_to "Cookie Policy", cookies_policy_path, class: "text-[#0F224F] font-medium underline hover:text-[#002d75]" %>.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-headline text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">8. Changes to this policy</h2>
          <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            We may update this policy from time to time. If we make significant changes, we'll let you know by email or through the website.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-headline text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">9. Contact us</h2>
          <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            If you have questions about this privacy policy or how we handle your data, <%= link_to "get in touch", contact_path, class: "text-[#0F224F] font-medium underline hover:text-[#002d75]" %>.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>
